  <title>2.2 Y-Axis Cooling</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">Y 轴冷却</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Y 轴滚珠螺母（位于十字滑块上）由 Z 轴滚珠丝杠支撑轴承冷却液供给。然后，冷却液将用于供给 Y 轴前轴承（位于底座上）冷却，然后再返回主轴温度控制器。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;"><image src="Z-Axis Ball Screw Support Bearing Cooling_1.png" scale="5.00%" width="2" height="2" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="Figure 2.3 Y-Axis Cooling.png" scale="60.00%" width="737" height="547" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
